[{"id":"ec25c1f1729a34f5a95b1682ac16873d","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: G2 ready","date":"2008-06-17T16:32:45.000Z","formatted_date":"Jun 17, 2008","formatted_time":"4:32 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: LVJET@aol.com [mailto:LVJET@aol.com] \nSent: Tuesday, June 17, 2008 12:06 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: G2 ready\n\n \n\nLesley,\n\nAsk Je if there is somebody he would like me to take for a ride in S76,\nI would like to fly it for 20 min today if he approves?  or I could just\nrun it on the ground and not fly.\n\n \n\ntell Je that Gulfstream will be completed at 9pm tonight and ready to\nfly. Waiting on Standby battery to charge only.\n\n \n\nFlight time to Paris is 6+45 with +32 wind., (at least 60kts tailwind\nfor non stop).\n\nFlight time to Zorro is 3+50 with - 45 wind.\n\n \n\nPlease advise when I should return to NY?\n\n \n\nZorro - weather is partly cloudy high of 92 with lows 62 in the evening,\ngreat all week.\n\nParis - Thursday partly cloudy 71 degrees high and 52 lows.\n\n             Friday - Rain.\n\n            Saturday and Sunday -partly cloudy\n\n            Monday - Rain.\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nGas prices getting you down? Search AOL Autos for fuel-efficient used\ncars <http://autos.aol.com/used?ncid=aolaut00050000000007> .\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavi